{"tid":1473891,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"中美有機會借助香港，進入和平議程","createTime":"2019-08-15T03:39:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T03:48:54.000Z","uid":232671,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"8201a02f5ccd457d86456db0b66c1c0954fcfd7b","tid":1473891,"uid":232671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T03:39:16.000Z","msg":"陳雲：中美有機會借助香港，進入和平議程，而且以香港民主做優先的合作試驗基地。這段空檔，至為危險！各位務必參考我的說話，暫停所有衝擊性質的社運，等候中美雙方和談。改為整理資料，製作文宣及短片宣傳，持續影響美國議員及民意，催谷《香港人權及民主法案》通過。<br />\n我們要民主，但也有人是不要的！香港民主是損害好多既得利益者的，目前在香港犯錯的官員在民主化之後也恐懼受到懲罰，故此一旦有衝擊性質的社運，必會有人騎劫或破壞，製造傷亡事件，故此各位前線的兄弟姐妹，請務必堅忍，暫停衝擊性質的社運。請將社運定格在星期日的完美受害人位置，不要輕舉妄動。<br />\n陳雲在此，正義必會降臨香港。"},{"pid":"5689455fc94009f2e3b63923be1b56fbbdd8746e","tid":1473891,"uid":217418,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T03:41:09.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">毋忘8月5號荃灣刀手斬人</span>"},{"pid":"12dbf0d8144af5c48bdc8ac4a09dfce3446aeb03","tid":1473891,"uid":171992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T03:41:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/6yR8ycR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6yR8ycR.jpg&h=a587efad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/14/141044_b70c4022f89dcf5617302fe3f20434af.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F14%2F141044_b70c4022f89dcf5617302fe3f20434af.jpeg&h=b7bac505&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/14/141056_6689ba9867dc55e5e3b796d75180758d.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F14%2F141056_6689ba9867dc55e5e3b796d75180758d.jpeg&h=42f5c084&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img 